RESEARCH CITATION:

This implementation is based on the research:
Chuderski, A. (2013). The relational integration task explains fluid reasoning
above and beyond other working memory tasks. Memory & Cognition, 42(3), 448-463.
https://doi.org/10.3758/s13421-013-0366-x

If you use this software for research purposes, please cite both this
implementation and the original research paper.
